      public Subject​(String subjectName, Collection<String> competencies, String certificationDate, String attestationForm, Collection<String> teachers, MarkType mark)
      Construct subject. Mark: 0 - failed, 1 - passed, 2-5 - common mark.
      Parameters:
      subjectName - the name of subject
      competencies - the competencies
      certificationDate - the date when person passed or got mark.
      attestationForm - the form of passing the subjects
      teachers - the persons who taught owner of this
      mark - the specific mark
